{
  "topicId": "m6-t2",
  "title": "Asking About Places and Services (Levantine)",
  "dialect": "levantine",
  "steps": [
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Asking 'Where is?'",
          "arabic": "السؤال عن 'وين؟'"
        },
        "text": "The most common way to ask 'Where is?' in Levantine Arabic is using \"وين؟\" (Wēn?). It's simple and direct, used for both people and objects, but here we focus on places.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "وين البنك؟",
            "english": "Where is the bank?",
            "transliteration": "Wēn il-bank?"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "وين المطعم؟",
            "english": "Where is the restaurant?",
            "transliteration": "Wēn il-maṭʿam?"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Expressing 'I want...'",
          "arabic": "التعبير عن 'أنا بدي...'"
        },
        "text": "To express 'I want' in Levantine, you use \"بدي\" (Biddī). This is a versatile verb used to indicate a desire for an object, a place, or an action.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "بدي قهوة.",
            "english": "I want coffee/a cafe.",
            "transliteration": "Biddī qahwe."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "بدي مطعم.",
            "english": "I want a restaurant.",
            "transliteration": "Biddī maṭʿam."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Naming a 'Place'",
          "arabic": "تسمية 'محل' أو 'مكان'"
        },
        "text": "The word for 'place' or 'location' is \"محل\" (Maḥall) or \"مكان\" (Makān). \"محل\" is very common in Levantine when referring to a specific shop or establishment.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "هاد محل جديد.",
            "english": "This is a new place/shop.",
            "transliteration": "Hād maḥall jdīd."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "في مكان هون؟",
            "english": "Is there a place here?",
            "transliteration": "Fī makān hōn?"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
